                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-58-off289 t18170416-58-cd290"></join>, two pair of shoes, value 18s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170416-58-victim451" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Hasler
                        <interp inst="t18170416-58-victim451" type="surname" value="Hasler"></interp>
