                     <interp inst="t18170416-58-verdict293" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 21.</p>
               <p>Of stealing, but not privately.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18170416-58-punish294" type="punishmentDescription">
